translated: Jernström, Rolf Ivar, livestock consultant, Växjö, b. 3rd of September in Tierp parish, Uppland County, son of Ivar J. and Hildur Olivia Eriksson. Married in 1933 to Zenta Björklund. Children: Margareta, born in 1938, Anders, born in 1942. - Graduated as an agricultural engineer in 1930, attended consultant courses in 1931. Teacher at Ultuna Agricultural School from 1931 to 1933, inspector at Hofors Agriculture from 1933 to 1934, teacher at Bjärka-Säby Agricultural School from 1934 to 1937, livestock consultant since 1911 at Kronoberg County. Member of the Royal Agricultural Society; domestic economy organization since 1937. Publications: Articles regarding livestock management in professional journals and documents.
